\p
\v 15 ThenВҰ126819 ShemuelВҰ126831 lay down \add again\add* untilВҰ126821 the morningВҰ126823 when he openedВҰ126824 the doorsВҰ126827 of Yahweh's houseВҰ126828 \add as usual\add*, \add вүҲbutВҰ126819\add* \add *he\add* was scared to tell EliВҰ126839 about the visionВҰ126836.
