\p
\v 17 вҖңWhat did he tell you?вҖқ \add @Eli\add* \add вүҲasked\add*. вҖңDon't hide it from me. May GodВҰ126867 \add вүҲpunish you severely\add* if you hide a \add single\add* wordВҰ126874 from \add вүҲeverything\add* he told you.вҖқ
\v 18 \add вүҲSoВҰ126883\add* ShemuelВҰ126886 told him \add вүҲeverything\add* without hiding anything. ThenВҰ126883 Eli \add вүҲanswered\add*, вҖңIt's YahwehВҰ126896. May he do \add вүҲwhatever he thinks best\add*.вҖқ
\p
\v 19 \add вүҲAs\add* ShemuelВҰ126905 grew up, YahwehВҰ126906 was with him and nothing he said failed to happen,
