\v 30 Actually, if the troopsВҰ131844 had eatenВҰ131842 what they'd foundВҰ131848 from the plunderВҰ131845 of theirВҰ131846 enemiesВҰ131846 today, how much better it would have been because \add вүҲwe might have had an even more decisive victory over the\add* PhilistinesВҰ131855.вҖқ
\p
\v 31 That dayВҰ131858 theyВҰ131857 killed PhilistinesВҰ131860 from Mikmas to Ayyalon, \add вүҲbutВҰ131857\add* the fighters were \add вүҲtotally exhaustedВҰ131863\add*.
\v 32 \add *They\add* rushedВҰ131867 greedily at the plunder, grabbing sheepВҰ131875, cattleВҰ131876, and calves which theyВҰ131874 slaughteredВҰ131879 \add вүҲright there\add* and ateВҰ131882 with the bloodВҰ131886 \add still in them\add*.
\v 33 ThenВҰ131888 King Sha'ulВҰ131889 was told, вҖңLook, the people are sinningВҰ131893 against YahwehВҰ131894 by eatingВҰ131895 \add meat\add* with the bloodВҰ131898 \add still in it\add*.вҖқ
\p вҖңYou've all actedВҰ131900 treacherouslyВҰ131900,вҖқ he \add вүҲrespondedВҰ131899\add*, вҖң\add вүҲNow,\add* roll a big stoneВҰ131905 \add over\add* to me.вҖқ\x + \xo 14:33: \xt Gen 9:4; Lev 7:26-27; 17:10-14; 19:26; Deu 12:16,23; 15:23.\x*
\v 34 ThenВҰ131908 \add *he\add* saidВҰ131908, вҖңGoВҰ131909 out amongВҰ131911 the \add вүҲwarriors\add* and tell them to bringВҰ131914 their \add вүҲanimals over here\add* to slaughter and to eatВҰ131922, so \add вүҲthey\add* don'tВҰ131923 sinВҰ131925 against YahwehВҰ131926 by eatingВҰ131927 \add meat withВҰ131911\add* the bloodВҰ131930 \add still inВҰ131911 it\add*.вҖқ SoВҰ131908 the people broughtВҰ131931 their \add вүҲanimals over\add* and slaughtered them thereВҰ131941.
\v 35 ThenВҰ131943 Sha'ulВҰ131944 built an altar to YahwehВҰ131946вҖ”\add вүҲit was the first one heВҰ131948 built\add*.
\rem /s1 Jonathan in Danger of Death
\p
\v 36 Then Sha'ulВҰ131955 said, вҖңLet's goВҰ131956 afterВҰ131957 the PhilistinesВҰ131958 tonight and plunderВҰ131961 them untilВҰ131964 the lightВҰ131966 of morningВҰ131967. Let's not leaveВҰ131970 \add вүҲany of them alive\add*.вҖқ
\p вҖңDo \add вүҲwhat you feel is right\add*,вҖқ they \add вүҲrespondedВҰ131954\add*.
\p \add вүҲButВҰ131954\add* the priestВҰ131981 said, вҖңLet's \add вүҲask GodВҰ131986 here first\add*.вҖқ
\p
\v 37 \add вүҲSoВҰ131988\add* Sha'ulВҰ131989 asked GodВҰ131990, вҖңShould \add #we\add* goВҰ131991 afterВҰ131992 the PhilistinesВҰ131993? Will youВҰ131994 giveВҰ131994 YisraelВҰ131996 \add вүҲvictory over them\add*?вҖқ \add вүҲButВҰ131988\add* \add @Yahweh\add* didn'tВҰ131997 answerВҰ131998 himВҰ131998 that dayВҰ131999.
