\v 39 As YahwehВҰ132020 who savesВҰ132021 YisraelВҰ132024 lives, even if it's my \add own\add* son Yonatan, \add whoever sinned today\add* will certainly die.вҖқ \add вүҲButВҰ132034 the peopleВҰ132038 didn'tВҰ132034 volunteer\add* \add any information\add*.
