\v 41 Then Sha'ul \add вүҲasked\add* Yisrael'sВҰ132072 godВҰ132071 YahwehВҰ132070, вҖң\add вүҲShow us the truth\add*.вҖқ And Sha'ul and Yonatan were selectedвҖ”not the peopleВҰ132078.\x + \xo 14:41: \xt Num 27:21; 1Sam 28:6.\x*
