\v 45 \add вүҲButВҰ132131\add* the people \add stood up to\add* Sha'ulВҰ132135, вҖңShould Yonatan die? \add вүҲWasn't it him who saved\add* YisraelВҰ132144 \add today\add*? \add вүҲWe won'tВҰ132168 stand for it\add*. As YahwehВҰ132148 lives, \add вүҲnot even a hair onВҰ132144 his headВҰ132153 will be touched\add* because he worked withВҰ132144 GodВҰ132159 today.вҖқ And \add so\add* the people rescued Yonatan andВҰ132131 he \add вүҲwasn't executed\add*.
