\v 46 Then Sha'ulВҰ132174 \add вүҲstopped chasingВҰ132175\add* the Philistines \add вүҲand wentВҰ132178 home\add*, and the Philistines \add also\add* returned to theirВҰ132179 placeВҰ132179.
\s1 Sha'ul's kingdom, and his family details
