\v 49 Sha'ul's sonsВҰ132223 were Yonatan, IshviВҰ132226, and Malki-Shua. His oldest daughterВҰ132232 was MerabВҰ132235, and the youngerВҰ132237 one was Mikal.
\v 50 His wife's name was AhinoamВҰ132243 (daughterВҰ132244 of Ahima'ats). His army commanderВҰ132248 was AbnerВҰ132251 (son of Sha'ul's uncleВҰ132255 NerВҰ132254вҖ”
\v 51 Kish was Sha'uls father, andВҰ132258 Abner'sВҰ132265 father NerВҰ132262 was Abiel'sВҰ132268 son).
