\v 52 The conflict with the PhilistinesВҰ132276 was intensive for all of Sha'uls life, \add вүҲso\add* whenever he sawВҰ132280 a \add вүҲgood warrior\add* or any strong, young manВҰ132284, then he would \add вүҲconscript\add* \add #them\add*.
\c 15
