\p
\v 1 \add One day\add* Shemuel saidВҰ132295 to Sha'ulВҰ132299, вҖңIt was YahwehВҰ132302 who sentВҰ132301 me to anointВҰ132303 you as kingВҰ132304 over his peopleВҰ132307 YisraelВҰ132310 \add back then\add*, \add вүҲso\add* now, listenВҰ132312 to \add вүҲwhat he has to say\add*.\x + \xo 15:1: \xt 1Sam 10:1.\x*
\v 2 Commander YahwehВҰ132320 saysВҰ132319, вҖҳI'veВҰ132322 noticed what \add вүҲthe Amalekites\add* did to YisraelВҰ132328 when they cameВҰ132334 out of EgyptВҰ132335вҖ”\add вүҲthey attacked them\add* \add as they passed by\add*.\x + \xo 15:2: \xt Exo 17:8-14; Deu 25:17-19.\x*
\v 3 \add вүҲSo\add* goВҰ132338 now and attackВҰ132339 AmalekВҰ132342 and destroyВҰ132343 \add #them\add* completely without compassionВҰ132352, putting men and women, children and infants to deathВҰ132354, along with \add their\add* cattle and sheepВҰ132366, camelsВҰ132367 and donkeysВҰ132370.вҖҷ вҖқ
\p
\v 4 \add вүҲSo\add* Sha'ulВҰ132374 summonedВҰ132373 the peopleВҰ132377 to TelaimВҰ132379 and counted them: twoВҰ132380 hundredВҰ132380 thousand footВҰ132382 soldiersВҰ132382 as well as tenВҰ132383 thousand \add вүҲwarriors\add* from YehudahВҰ132388.
