\v 6 ThenВҰ132399 \add *he\add* \add вүҲwarned\add* the Kenites, вҖң\add вүҲYou all need to move out from among\add* the Amalekites, \add вүҲso that you all won't be attacked along withВҰ132422 them\add*. \add вүҲThat's because you all were kind to our ancestors\add* when they cameВҰ132422 out of EgyptВҰ132423.вҖқ \add вүҲSoВҰ132399\add* the Kenites \add вүҲmoved out from among the Amalekites\add*.
