\v 7 ThenВҰ132429 Sha'ulВҰ132430 \add вүҲslaughtered the AmalekitesВҰ132433\add* from HavilahВҰ132434 to ShurВҰ132436 (near EgyptВҰ132441),
\v 8 andВҰ132451 \add #they\add* capturedВҰ132443 KingВҰ132449 AgagВҰ132446 aliveВҰ132450 \add вүҲbutВҰ132443\add* killed everyoneВҰ132455 else with swordsВҰ132459.
\v 9 \add вүҲHoweverВҰ132462, as well as sparing\add* AgagВҰ132466, they \add вүҲtook\add* the best sheepВҰ132470 andВҰ132461 cattleВҰ132471
\s1 God rejects Sha'ul
