\p
\v 10 \add вүҲThen\add* YahwehВҰ132496 \add вүҲtold\add* Shemuel,
\v 11 вҖңI regretВҰ132502 that I'veВҰ132505 \add вүҲappointed\add* Sha'ulВҰ132508 as king because he's turnedВҰ132512 \add вүҲaway from followingВҰ132513\add* me and hasn't \add вүҲobeyed my instructionsВҰ132516\add*.вҖқ \add вүҲThat really upset\add* ShemuelВҰ132520 and he criedВҰ132521 out to YahwehВҰ132524 all nightВҰ132527.
\v 12 Early the next morningВҰ132533, ShemuelВҰ132530 \add вүҲgot up\add* to meet Sha'ul, \add вүҲbutВҰ132529 someone\add* told \add *him\add*, вҖңSha'ul went to KarmelВҰ132540, and wow, he set up a monumentВҰ132544 to himself. ThenВҰ132529 he turnedВҰ132545 around and went to GilgalВҰ132548.вҖқ
