\v 14 вҖңThenВҰ132567 what's \add вүҲthat bleating of sheepВҰ132572 that I can hear\add*?вҖқ \add вүҲasked\add* ShemuelВҰ132568. вҖңAnd \add вүҲI'm sure I can hear cattleВҰ132576 soundsВҰ132570 too\add*?вҖқ
