\v 15 вҖң\add Ah,\add* \add вүҲthe warriors took\add* them from the AmalekitesВҰ132583,вҖқ Sha'ulВҰ132582 \add вүҲanswered\add*. вҖңThey \add вүҲwanted to save\add* the best of the sheepВҰ132591 andВҰ132581 the cattleВҰ132592 in order to sacrificeВҰ132594 to yourВҰ132596 godВҰ132596 YahwehВҰ132595. \add вүҲButВҰ132581\add* weВҰ132600 completely destroyedВҰ132600 the rest.вҖқ
\p
\v 16 вҖңStop,вҖқ said ShemuelВҰ132604, вҖңand let me tell you what YahwehВҰ132614 \add вүҲtold me last\add* nightВҰ132616.вҖқ
\p вҖң\add вүҲGo ahead\add*,вҖқ \add @Sha'ul\add* \add вүҲrespondedВҰ132603\add*.
\p
\v 17 \add вүҲSo\add* Shemuel told \add him\add*, вҖңAlthough you \add вүҲconsider yourself insignificant\add*, aren'tВҰ132625 you the head of the tribesВҰ132632 of Yisrael? YahwehВҰ132636 anointedВҰ132635 you as kingВҰ132637 over Yisrael,
\v 18 thenВҰ132642 sentВҰ132642 youВҰ132642 \add вүҲoff withВҰ132644 the task of completely destroying the sinful AmalekitesВҰ132643вҖ”fightingВҰ132654 untilВҰ132656 theyВҰ132657 were all destroyedВҰ132657\add*.
\v 19 \add вүҲSoВҰ132660\add* why didn'tВҰ132661 you \add вүҲobey Yahweh's command\add*? \add вүҲInstead,\add* you \add вүҲheaded straight for the plunderВҰ132669 andВҰ132660 disobeyed Yahweh\add*.вҖқ
