\v 20 вҖңI \add вүҲdid listenВҰ132682 to Yahweh's instructions\add*,вҖқ Sha'ulВҰ132677 \add вүҲinsisted\add*. вҖңand \add вүҲI did what he asked\add*. \add вүҲSo now\add* I've broughtВҰ132691 Amalekite KingВҰ132695 AgagВҰ132694 \add here\add* and I've completely destroyedВҰ132700 the Amalekites.
\v 21 \add Yes,\add* the peopleВҰ132703 \add вүҲkept some of the best\add* sheepВҰ132705 andВҰ132706 cattleВҰ132706 to sacrificeВҰ132709 to yourВҰ132711 godВҰ132711 YahwehВҰ132710 here atВҰ132712 GilgalВҰ132712.вҖқ
\p
\v 22 \add вүҲButВҰ132714\add* ShemuelВҰ132715 \add вүҲasked\add*,
\q1 вҖңIs YahwehВҰ132717 \add вүҲhappier\add* with burntВҰ132718 offeringsВҰ132718 andВҰ132719 sacrifices
\q1 than \add вүҲwith those who follow his instructions\add*?
