\q1
\v 23 Rebellion is as sinful as doing sorcery,
\q1 вүҲand being stubborn is as sinful as worshipping idols.
\q1 Because you have rejected Yahweh's \add вүҲinstructions\add*,
\q1 вүҲhe has rejected you as kingВҰ132746.вҖқ
