\p
\v 24 вҖң\add Yes,\add* I've sinnedВҰ132754,вҖқ Sha'ulВҰ132750 \add вүҲrespondedВҰ132749\add*. вҖң\add I can see that\add* I've \add вүҲdisobeyed Yahweh's instruction, and yours too\add*, because I fearedВҰ132767 the peopleВҰ132770 and \add вүҲdid what they were requesting\add*.
\v 25 \add вүҲButВҰ132774\add* now, pleaseВҰ132776 forgiveВҰ132775 my sinВҰ132779 andВҰ132774 come back with me so IВҰ132777 can worshipВҰ132782 YahwehВҰ132783.вҖқ
\p
\v 26 вҖң\add No,\add* I won'tВҰ132790 returnВҰ132791 with you.вҖқ ShemuelВҰ132786 \add вүҲreplied\add*. вҖңYou've rejected Yahweh's \add вүҲinstructions\add*, andВҰ132785 Yahweh has \add already\add* rejected you as Yisrael'sВҰ132805 kingВҰ132802.вҖқ
