\v 27 \add вүҲAs\add* ShemuelВҰ132809 turnedВҰ132808 around to goВҰ132810, \add @Sha'ul\add* grabbed the edge of his robeВҰ132814 and itВҰ132815 tore.\x + \xo 15:27-28: \xt 1Sam 28:17; 1Ki 11:30-31.\x*
\v 28 вҖңToday, YahwehВҰ132821 has torn the kingdom of YisraelВҰ132825 away from you,вҖқ ShemuelВҰ132819 told him. вҖңAnd he's givenВҰ132828 it to \add вүҲanother man who's\add* betterВҰ132830 than you.
\v 29 And \add вүҲby the way\add*, Yisrael'sВҰ132835 powerful \add God\add* doesn't \add вүҲgo back on his word\add*, andВҰ132838 doesn't changeВҰ132844 his mind \add вүҲlike people tend to do\add*.
\p
\v 30 вҖң\add It's true that\add* I'veВҰ132847 sinnedВҰ132847,вҖқ Sha'ul saidВҰ132846, вҖң\add butВҰ132846\add* pleaseВҰ132850 honourВҰ132849 me now in front of the Israeli peopleВҰ132854 andВҰ132846 their eldersВҰ132852. And thenВҰ132846 returnВҰ132857 with me, so I can worshipВҰ132859 yourВҰ132861 godВҰ132861 YahwehВҰ132860.вҖқ
