\m And SamuelВҰ132895 hackedВҰ132905 AgagВҰ132909 to piecesВҰ132905 \add вүҲinВҰ132912 frontВҰ132910\add* of YahwehВҰ132911 \add there\add* atВҰ132912 GilgalВҰ132912.
\p
\v 34 ThenВҰ132924 ShemuelВҰ132916 went \add home\add* to RamahВҰ132917, and Sha'ulВҰ132918 returned to his houseВҰ132922 in GibeahВҰ132923.
\v 35 \add After that,\add* ShemuelВҰ132929 never saw Sha'ul again, butВҰ132926 he mournedВҰ132940 for him, andВҰ132926 YahwehВҰ132945 regrettedВҰ132946 that he'd made Sha'ul kingВҰ132949 over YisraelВҰ132955.
\c 16
\s1 Shemuel anoints David as King
\rem /s1 David Anointed as King; Samuel Anoints David as King; Samuel Anoints David; David Is Anointed King
\s4 Full kingdom
\p
\v 1 Then YahwehВҰ132959 spoke to ShemuelВҰ132962, вҖң\add вүҲHow long are you going to keep mourningВҰ132967 for Sha'ulВҰ132970 for\add*, when I myself have rejectedВҰ132972 him as king over YisraelВҰ132976? Fill your horn withВҰ132991 oil and go. I'llВҰ132981 send you to YishayВҰ132984 (Jesse) from Bethlehem, because I'veВҰ132990 seen \add вүҲone of his sons who'd make a\add* \add good\add* king for me.вҖқ
\p
\v 2 вҖңHow can I \add вүҲdo that\add*?вҖқ \add вүҲasked\add* ShemuelВҰ132996. вҖңSha'ulВҰ133000 would killВҰ133001 me if he heard about it.вҖқ
\p вҖңTake a heiferВҰ133005 \add вүҲwithВҰ133008 you\add*,вҖқ Yahweh said, вҖңandВҰ132995 say, вҖҳI'veВҰ133012 comeВҰ133012 to sacrificeВҰ133010 to Yahweh.вҖҷ
\v 3 \add вүҲInvite\add* YishayВҰ133015 to the sacrificeВҰ133016, and I'llВҰ133028 show you what do to \add вүҲfrom there\add*, and you should anointВҰ133023 the one I tell you to.вҖқ
\p
\v 4 \add вүҲSoВҰ133031\add* Shemuel did what YahwehВҰ133036 had told him, and wentВҰ133037 to Bethlehem. The townВҰ133042 eldersВҰ133041 trembledВҰ133040 when they met him, and \add вүҲasked\add*, вҖңDo you comeВҰ133046 in peaceВҰ133045?вҖқ
\p
\v 5 вҖң\add Yes,\add* inВҰ133057 peaceВҰ133050,вҖқ he \add вүҲanswered\add* вҖңI'veВҰ133053 come to sacrifice to YahwehВҰ133052. Purify yourselvesВҰ133054 and come withВҰ133057 me to the sacrifice.вҖқ ThenВҰ133048 he purified YishayВҰ133061 and his sonsВҰ133064 and calledВҰ133065 them to the sacrifice.
