\v 12 \f + \fr 17:12 \ft Verses 12вҖ“31 aren't included in every ancient Greek translation.\f*\add вүҲNow\add* DavidВҰ133598 was the son of YishayВҰ133608 (from the Efrat clan, he lived in Bethlehem in YehudahВҰ133606) who had eightВҰ133610 sonsВҰ133611, and by Sha'ul's timeВҰ133613, was quite old compared to other menВҰ133617.\f + \fr 17:12 \ft There's a small variation in the original manuscripts at the end of the verse, but it has minimal effect on the essential story-line.\f*
