\v 17 \add One day\add* YishayВҰ133678 said to his son DavidВҰ133679, вҖң\add вүҲHere's a sack\add* of roastedВҰ133686 grainВҰ133686 and ten loaves of breadВҰ133689. Take them straight away to your brothers at the camp.
