\v 20 \add вүҲSoВҰ133727\add* DavidВҰ133728 got up earlyВҰ133727 inВҰ133729 the morningВҰ133729 and left the flockВҰ133733 withВҰ133729 a \add вүҲshepherd\add*, and set out just like YishayВҰ133741 had toldВҰ133740 him to. \add вүҲWhenВҰ133731\add* he got to the battleground and the campВҰ133743, the \add вүҲwarriors\add* were just goingВҰ133745 out to the battle line and they were shoutingВҰ133749 \add вүҲthe battle cryВҰ133749\add*.
