\v 24 \add вүҲButВҰ133799 when\add* the IsraelisВҰ133801 sawВҰ133802 the \add вүҲchampion\add*, theyВҰ133802 were \add вүҲterrified\add* andВҰ133799 fled \add вүҲaway from himВҰ133807\add*.
\v 25 saying \add to each other\add*, вҖңHave you seen this man who's coming out? He's certainly coming to mock YisraelВҰ133814! Any man who can defeat him will be made very wealthyВҰ133830 by the kingВҰ133831, andВҰ133811 he'll give his daughterВҰ133837 to him, plusВҰ133825 \add вүҲhis extended family will be exempt from paying taxes\add*.вҖқ
