\v 26 вҖңWhat \add was it that'll\add* be done for the manВҰ133859 who \add вүҲkills\add* this Philistine andВҰ133848 take's Yisrael'sВҰ133869 disgrace away?вҖқ DavidВҰ133849 asked some of the menВҰ133852 standingВҰ133853 around him. вҖңBecause who does that uncircumcisedВҰ133873 Philistine \add think he is\add* that he would taunt the \add вүҲarmy\add* of the livingВҰ133879 GodВҰ133878?вҖқ
