\v 28 \add вүҲButВҰ133893 when\add* David'sВҰ133905 oldestВҰ133896 brother EliabВҰ133894 heard him talking to the menВҰ133900, \add вүҲhe got very angry\add* and \add вүҲscolded\add* him, вҖңWhy have you come down here? Who's looking after thoseВҰ133918 few sheepВҰ133917 that you left inВҰ133897 the desert? I know you \add вүҲhave a big head\add* and \add вүҲyou're just a troublemaker\add*вҖ”you \add just\add* want to watch the battleВҰ133931.вҖқ
