\v 35 and I would go afterВҰ134034 it and \add вүҲbeat it\add* and rescueВҰ134036 \add <the sheep\add* from its mouthВҰ134037. If it \add вүҲwentВҰ134033 to attack\add* me, thenВҰ134033 I'd grasp it by the jaw and beat it and killВҰ134043 it.
