\v 46 Today, YahwehВҰ134260 will \add вүҲhelp me defeat you\add* and I'll knock you down and cut off your headВҰ134266. \add вүҲWhat's more,\add* I'll giveВҰ134268 the Philistine army corpsesВҰ134269 to the \add вүҲvultures and wild animalsВҰ134276\add* today, then \add вүҲeveryone\add* will knowВҰ134278 that there'sВҰ134283 a godВҰ134284 inВҰ134261 YisraelВҰ134285.
\v 47 \add вүҲEveryoneВҰ134300 here will learn\add* that YahwehВҰ134298 doesn't save withВҰ134295 swordsВҰ134295 or spearsВҰ134296, because \add *he's\add* inВҰ134295 charge of the battleВҰ134301 andВҰ134287 will \add вүҲhelp us defeat\add* youВҰ134303 all.вҖқ
