\v 49 \add *He\add* \add вүҲslipped\add* his handВҰ134326 into his bag and took out a single stone and slungВҰ134333 it towards the PhilistineВҰ134337вҖ”striking him onВҰ134343 the forehead. TheВҰ134323 stone sank into his forehead and he collapsed forwards onto the groundВҰ134348,
