\v 51 DavidВҰ134369 ranВҰ134368 and stoodВҰ134370 over the PhilistineВҰ134373вҖ”drawing \add @Goliat's\add* swordВҰ134377 out of its sheathВҰ134379 to kill himВҰ134380 and cut off his headВҰ134386.\x + \xo 17:51: \xt 2Sam 21:19.\x*
