\p WhenВҰ134368 the PhilistinesВҰ134388 sawВҰ134387 that theirВҰ134392 powerful championВҰ134392 was dead, they fled
\v 52 and the \add вүҲIsraeliВҰ134397 warriorsВҰ134396 started yelling\add* and theyВҰ134411 chased the Philistines into the valleyВҰ134407 and as far as the gatesВҰ134409 of Ekron. The \add вүҲdead bodies\add* of the Philistines \add could be seen\add* onВҰ134414 the road all the wayВҰ134414 from ShaaraimВҰ134415 to GatВҰ134418 and Ekron.
\v 53 \add вүҲWhenВҰ134430 the IsraelisВҰ134425\add* returnedВҰ134423 from chasingВҰ134426 the PhilistinesВҰ134428, they \add вүҲraided the valuables\add* from theirВҰ134432 camp.
\v 54 DavidВҰ134435 put \add @Goliat's\add* equipment into his \add own\add* tentВҰ134446, thenВҰ134434 he carried his headВҰ134438 to Jerusalem.
\s1 Sha'ul asks about David
