\v 28 Please forgive your femaleВҰ138908 servant \add вүҲfor being forward\add* because Yahweh will certain \add вүҲadvance my master's reputation\add*. My master is fightingВҰ138922 Yahweh's battlesВҰ138919 and \add вүҲall your life, you haven't broken the law\add*.
\v 29 \add вүҲEvenВҰ138945 if someone decides to chase you andВҰ138930 try to kill you my masterВҰ138939, your godВҰ138946 YahwehВҰ138939 will keep you wrapped inВҰ138942 his\add* bundleВҰ138942 of the livingВҰ138943, \add вүҲwhereas\add* your enemiesВҰ138949 will be \add вүҲslung away like stones from a sling\add*.
