\v 43 DavidВҰ139228 had also married AhinoamВҰ139226 from Yizre'elВҰ139229, \add вүҲso\add* both of them becameВҰ139230 his wivesВҰ139235.
\v 44 (\add вүҲMeanwhile\add* Sha'ulВҰ139238 had givenВҰ139239 his daughterВҰ139243, David' wifeВҰ139244 Mikal, to PaltiВҰ139246, Layish'sВҰ139249 son from GallimВҰ139251.)\x + \xo 25:44: \xt 2Sam 3:14-16.\x*
\c 26
