\p
\v 1 \add One time some\add* ZifitesВҰ139254 wentВҰ139253 to Sha'ulВҰ139257 atВҰ139263 GibeahВҰ139258 andВҰ139253 told \add <him\add*, вҖңIsn't DavidВҰ139261 hidingВҰ139262 himselfВҰ139262 onВҰ139263 the HakilahВҰ139264 hill \add вүҲopposite\add* YeshimonВҰ139267?вҖқ\x + \xo 26:1: \xt Psa 54 header.\x*
