\v 9 вҖңDon't \add вүҲkillВҰ139451\add* himВҰ139451,вҖқ DavidВҰ139445 \add вүҲrespondedВҰ139444\add*, вҖңbecause who \add вүҲcan attack\add* Yahweh's anointedВҰ139456 \add вүҲking\add* andВҰ139444 \add вүҲbe considered\add* innocent?вҖқ
\v 10 As YahwehВҰ139465 lives, he will certainly strikeВҰ139470 him, or \add else\add* his \add вүҲtime\add* will comeВҰ139474 and he'll dieВҰ139475, or \add maybe\add* he'll goВҰ139478 into battleВҰ139477 and be swept away.
