\v 12 \add вүҲSoВҰ139505\add* DavidВҰ139506 tookВҰ139505 the spearВҰ139509 and waterВҰ139513 jug that were near Sha'ul's headВҰ139514 and thenВҰ139505 \add вүҲgot out of there\add*. No one sawВҰ139519 them, and no one woke up or realisedВҰ139519, because YahwehВҰ139529 had \add вүҲcaused them all to fall into\add* a deep sleepВҰ139526.
