\v 13 ThenВҰ139533 DavidВҰ139534 \add вүҲcrossed the valley\add* andВҰ139536 stoodВҰ139536 on the top of the \add opposite\add* hillвҖ”\add вүҲquite a distanceВҰ139542 away\add*
\v 14 and called out to Abner and \add вүҲthe camp\add*, вҖңWon't you answerВҰ139560, Abner?вҖқ
