\v 15 вҖңAren't you a \add вүҲwarrior\add*?вҖқ DavidВҰ139574 \add вүҲcalled out\add*. вҖңAnd who inВҰ139584 YisraelВҰ139584 is \add вүҲas good as\add* you? ButВҰ139573 why didn'tВҰ139578 you watch over your master the king? Because one of the peopleВҰ139596 came to destroyВҰ139597 the king your master.
