\p
\v 1 \add вүҲButВҰ139839\add* DavidВҰ139840 \add вүҲthought to himself\add*, вҖң\add вүҲOne of these days, I'm going to be caught off-guard by Sha'ul's actions\add*. There's no \add вүҲfuture\add* for me \add here\add*, \add вүҲso\add* I definitely \add need to\add* slip away to the PhilistinesВҰ139863 regionВҰ139862. Then \add hopefully\add* Sha'ul will \add вүҲgive up looking for\add* me againВҰ139868 \add вүҲacross\add* all YisraelВҰ139872, and I'llВҰ139845 slip \add вүҲbe able to stay under his radar\add*.вҖқ
