\v 5 \add One day,\add* DavidВҰ139932 \add вүҲasked\add* Akish, вҖңIf I'veВҰ139939 foundВҰ139939 favourВҰ139940 in your eyesВҰ139941, \add вүҲask\add* them to giveВҰ139942 me a placeВҰ139945 in one of the citiesВҰ139947 in the countrysideВҰ139948 \add вүҲso\add* I can liveВҰ139949 thereВҰ139950. \add вүҲThere's no need for us to bludge onВҰ139941 youВҰ139956 here in the royalВҰ139955 cityВҰ139954\add*.вҖқ
