\v 8 and \add during that time\add*, \add *he\add* would take his menВҰ139992 to raid the GeshuritesВҰ139996, the Girzites, and the AmalekitesВҰ139999. They had lived in \add вүҲthat regionВҰ140010 from longВҰ140005 before\add*вҖ”from ShurВҰ140007 \add вүҲall the way to\add* EgyptВҰ140011.
\v 9 WhenВҰ140013 DavidВҰ140014 \add вүҲattackedВҰ140013 a place\add*, he would takeВҰ140022 the sheepВҰ140023 and cattleВҰ140024, donkeysВҰ140025 and camelsВҰ140026, and clothesВҰ140027, \add вүҲbutВҰ140013\add* he didn'tВҰ140018 leave \add вүҲanyone\add* alive. ThenВҰ140013 he'd returnВҰ140028 home and \add вүҲvisit\add* AkishВҰ140032.
