\p
\v 1 \add Meanwhile,\add* the Philistines were battling againstВҰ141510 YisraelВҰ141510, and the \add вүҲIsraelisВҰ141513\add* fled from the Philistines \add вүҲbutВҰ141508\add* \add many\add* \add вүҲwere killed\add* onВҰ141510 MtВҰ141518. GilboaВҰ141519.
